## Overview

This is a content site that aggregates podcast, videos, and other types of media.

## Tech Stack

Typescript is used for everything
- Frontend: Next.js 15, Tailwind, Shadcn, Framer Motion
- Backend: Postgres, Supabase, Drizzle ORM, Server Actions
- Auth: Supabase Auth
- Deployment: Vercel
- Package Manager: Bun